data.description: This 5 bedroom, 3 full bath chink log cabin has TOTAL privacy! The main level has beautiful oak floors throughout, LR w/fireplace (unvented w/gas logs), DR, spacious Kitchen with NEW GRANITE COUNTERS, plenty of cabinets, bar, Stainless refrigerator, range, microwave, & dishwasher, and Main BR & BA (jacuzzi tub, 2 sinks, separate shower); the Upper floor houses two very spacious BRs & BA (2 sinks, shower/tub combo); Terrace level - 2 BRs & BA (2 sinks, shower/tub combo) and two nice Bonus Rooms (Den, Game Room, Office, Theatre Room, etc, or anything your family wants). HOME HAS JUST BEEN RESTAINED. There is a seasonal mtn and lake view & porches for you to enjoy all year long. Extras include metal roof, fire pit, 2-car carport, small creek on property, 2 laundry rooms & gated community. Rentals are allowed (both short term and long term).
